    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  To distinguish correlation from causation, we performed\n                  <jats:italic>in-silico</jats:italic>\n                  analyses of three COVID-19 outcomes (N&gt;1,000,000). We show genetic correlation and putative causality with depressive symptoms, metformin use, and alcohol use. COVID-19 risk loci associated with several hematologic biomarkers. Comprehensive findings inform genetic contributions to COVID-19 epidemiology, molecular mechanisms, and risk factors.\n                </jats:p>",
